Johannesburg &#8211; A 27-year-old man is expected to appear in the Johannesburg Magistrate&#8217;s Court on Friday after the burnt body of his 22-year-old ex-girlfriend was found in a veld in Lyndhurst, Johannesburg.Mokoena was allegedly killed and burnt by her ex-boyfriend after she was reported missing on April 28.She was enrolled as a part-time student.Police discovered her body on April 29.